request.description:
Track complaint status.

**Endpoint:** POST /api/ba/complaintTracking

**TESTED Request Body:**
- `reqData.complaintTrackingReq.complaintType`: Type of complaint (e.g., "Service")
- `reqData.complaintTrackingReq.complaintId`: Complaint ID from complaintRegistration response (e.g., "XD1495446616192")

**Response:**
```json
{
  "reqData": {
    "complaintTrackingReq": {
      "complaintType": "Service",
      "complaintId": "XD1495446616192"
    }
  }
}
```
